                "game-obj": "Traits",
                "game-id": "7053ba2c0f6250d9ffc4461c5a6c60b3",
                "text": "A type of feat that any character can select, regardless of ancestry and class, as long as they meet the prerequisites. You can select a feat with this trait when your class grants a general feat."
            },
